The aim of the project is to help connect translators with wider audience.


Global setup:

 Download and install Git
  git config --global user.name "Your Name"
  git config --global user.email jakupovic@gmail.com
  Add your public key
        

Next steps:

  mkdir sos-translate
  cd sos-translate
  git init
  touch README
  git add README
  git commit -m 'first commit'
  git remote add origin git@github.com:jakupovic/sos-translate.git
  git push origin master
      

Existing Git Repo?

  cd existing_git_repo
  git remote add origin git@github.com:jakupovic/sos-translate.git
  git push origin master
      
When you're done:

  http://github.com/jakupovic/sos-translate


